data.description: ONE OF THE BEST VALUES IN LEHIGH ACRES.  This home sold for $268,600 when new in 2006..Beautiful, Newer Lennar Home with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths and a 2 Car Garage, located in the desirable Greenbriar Subdivision of Lehigh Acres. Greenbriar is an area predominately populated with all new, well maintained homes. Your most valued clients will be impressed with the like-new condition of this home. The home features a separate living room and formal dining room with vaulted ceilings and a family room off the kitchen with sliding glass doors out to the very large backyard in one of the nicest areas of Lehigh Acres.  Kitchen features tile floors, upgraded wood cabinets and solid-surface counter-tops and all appliances. This home has been newly remodeled and professionally painted inside and out, has new carpet and is MOVE-IN ready for immediate occupancy. Quiet neighborhood with a country feel.Great home for bringing up children. Convenient to Joel Blvd. and State Road 82.
